<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Thank you — J Beaver's Jewels</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<script src="config.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #f5ede1;
    --paper: #fbf6ec;
    --ink: #1f140d;
    --burgundy: #6b1f2a;
    --gold: #b8884c;
    --muted: #8a7560;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  body::before {
    content: "J";
    position: fixed;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 80vh;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    opacity: 0.04;
    z-index: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .card {
    max-width: 580px;
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid rgba(31, 20, 13, 0.12);
    padding: 4.5rem 3.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .ornament {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 1rem;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  h1 em { color: var(--burgundy); font-style: italic; }
  .lead {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .details {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(31, 20, 13, 0.12);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(31, 20, 13, 0.12);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .details strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .details a {
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(31, 20, 13, 0.2);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }
  .details a:hover { color: var(--burgundy); }
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--cream);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    transition: all 0.4s;
  }
  .btn:hover {
    background: var(--burgundy);
    border-color: var(--burgundy);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="ornament">&#10022; &#10022; &#10022;</div>
  <div class="eyebrow">Order Confirmed</div>
  <h1>Thank you <em>kindly.</em></h1>
  <p class="lead">Your order has been received and a confirmation is on its way to your inbox.</p>
  <p class="lead">Each piece is hand checked at the atelier and dispatched within 1 to 2 business days. You will receive an insured tracking number the moment your parcel ships.</p>
  <div class="details">
    <strong>Questions about your order?</strong>
    Email <a class="cfg-email-link"></a> or call <a class="cfg-phone-link"></a>. <span class="cfg-hours-1"></span>.
  </div>
  <a href="/" class="btn">Return to the Collection</a>
</div>

<script>
  const c = window.SITE_CONFIG || {};
  if (c.email) {
    document.querySelectorAll(".cfg-email-link").forEach(el => {
      el.href = "mailto:" + c.email;
      el.textContent = c.email;
    });
  }
  if (c.phoneRaw) {
    document.querySelectorAll(".cfg-phone-link").forEach(el => {
      el.href = "tel:" + c.phoneRaw;
      el.textContent = c.phone || c.phoneRaw;
    });
  }
  document.querySelectorAll(".cfg-hours-1").forEach(el => { el.textContent = c.hoursLine1 || ""; });
</script>

</body>
</html>
